name: Jackhammer Project
summary: Learn about .JMF files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: You should save your level in Jackhammer in the JMF format. Use the RMF format to export your map from Jackhammer to the Valve Hammer Editor.

description: Native project format created by Jackhammer, a level and map editor for games with quake-style BSP architecture; stores a level and all related information, which includes map sources.
